2. Ref 31946 (Sachsen)
[This report presents follow-up report no. 4 of a West Nile fever event in Germany's province Sachsen that started 13 Aug 2019. It includes the following outbreak summary as of 25 Sep 2019, and a map presenting the 16 outbreaks (with 22 cases).]

